001package edu.cnm.deepdive.spaceseek.model.entity;
002
003import androidx.annotation.NonNull;
004import androidx.room.ColumnInfo;
005import androidx.room.Entity;
006import androidx.room.Index;
007import androidx.room.PrimaryKey;
008import com.google.gson.annotations.Expose;
009import com.google.gson.annotations.SerializedName;
010import java.net.URL;
011import java.time.LocalDate;
012
013@Entity(
014    tableName = "apod",
015    indices = {
016        @Index(value = {"date"}, unique = true)
017    }
018)
019public class Apod {
020
021  @PrimaryKey(autoGenerate = true)
022  @ColumnInfo(name = "apod_id")
023  private long id;
024
025  @ColumnInfo(index = true, collate = ColumnInfo.NOCASE)
026  @Expose
027  @NonNull
028  private String title;
029
030  @ColumnInfo(collate = ColumnInfo.NOCASE)
031  @Expose
032  @SerializedName("explanation")
033  private String description;
034
035  @Expose
036  @NonNull
037  private LocalDate date;
038
039  @Expose
040  private String copyright;
041
042  @ColumnInfo(name = "media_type", index = true)
043  @Expose
044  @SerializedName("media_type")
045  @NonNull
046  private MediaType mediaType;
047
048  @ColumnInfo(name = "low_def_url")
049  @Expose
050  @SerializedName("url")
051  @NonNull
052  private URL lowDefUrl;
053
054  @ColumnInfo(name = "high_def_url")
055  @Expose
056  @SerializedName("hdurl")
057  private URL highDefUrl;
058
059  @ColumnInfo(name = "location")
060  @Expose
061  private String location;
062
063  @ColumnInfo(name = "is_favorite")
064  private boolean favorite;
065
066  public long getId() {
067    return id;
068  }
069
070  public void setId(long id) {
071    this.id = id;
072  }
073
074  @NonNull
075  public String getTitle() {
076    return title;
077  }
078
079  public void setTitle(@NonNull String title) {
080    this.title = title;
081  }
082
083  public String getDescription() {
084    return description;
085  }
086
087  public void setDescription(String description) {
088    this.description = description;
089  }
090
091  @NonNull
092  public LocalDate getDate() {
093    return date;
094  }
095
096  public void setDate(@NonNull LocalDate date) {
097    this.date = date;
098  }
099
100  public String getCopyright() {
101    return copyright;
102  }
103
104  public void setCopyright(String copyright) {
105    this.copyright = copyright;
106  }
107
108  @NonNull
109  public MediaType getMediaType() {
110    return mediaType;
111  }
112
113  public void setMediaType(@NonNull MediaType mediaType) {
114    this.mediaType = mediaType;
115  }
116
117  @NonNull
118  public URL getLowDefUrl() {
119    return lowDefUrl;
120  }
121
122  public void setLowDefUrl(@NonNull URL lowDefUrl) {
123    this.lowDefUrl = lowDefUrl;
124  }
125
126  public URL getHighDefUrl() {
127    return highDefUrl;
128  }
129
130  public void setHighDefUrl(URL highDefUrl) {
131    this.highDefUrl = highDefUrl;
132  }
133
134  public String getLocation() {
135    return location;
136  }
137
138  public void setLocation(String location) {
139    this.location = location;
140  }
141
142  public boolean isFavorite() {
143    return favorite;
144  }
145
146  public void setFavorite(boolean favorite) {
147    this.favorite = favorite;
148  }
149
150  public enum MediaType {
151    @SerializedName("image")
152    IMAGE(true),
153    @SerializedName("video")
154    VIDEO(false);
155
156    private final boolean downloadable;
157
158    MediaType(boolean downloadable) {
159      this.downloadable = downloadable;
160    }
161
162    public boolean isDownloadable() {
163      return downloadable;
164    }
165
166  }
167
168}
